Turner: Murdoch May Have to Leave News Corp. Helm

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-20T14:21:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/turner-murdoch-may-have-to-leave-helm-of-news-corp-.html
Billionaire  Ted Turner , chairman of
Turner Enterprises Inc., talks about the future of  News Corp . 
Chairman and Chief Executive Officer  Rupert Murdoch .  Turner, speaking with Betty Liu on Bloomberg Television's 
"In the Loop," said Murdoch will probably have to leave the helm
of his media company after a phone-hacking scandal that began at
one of its newspapers. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:00
 